# Default for a new experiment: don't track inference outputs.
# If you want to freeze and commit this experiment's records (e.g.
# so a future experiment can inherit them), add explicit exceptions:
#
#   !results/                                  # (un-ignore the whole dir)
#   !results/**/*.json
#
# Keep metrics/ and report/ committed — they're small, auditable, and
# define what the experiment claims.
results/
